---
title: Pork Meatballs & Indian Coconut Sauce  with Bombay Potatoes & Slaw
description: Explore a flavour fusion like no other – classic pork meatballs with an Indian-inspired twist. Gently spiced pork, Bombay potatoes and crunchy slaw all tied together in a creamy coconut sauce, this unlikely pairing will catch you by surprise as the flavours meld together in the most exquisite way.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with carrot due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
